reviewText: I love anything by Dr. Deb. Her teaching/writing style works for me. If you want to become a better judge of horse conformation she is the one to explain it so you can easily understand.
Item was in very good shape. I watched the entire DVD within a couple of days and it viewed fine, no skipping of freezing. A good buy!
Gives a down to earth, easy to understand assessment of conformation.  Her approach is easy for youth to understand and apply.
